VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (?i)^ARG\s+(?:PASSWORD|SECRET|API_KEY|APIKEY|TOKEN|ACCESS_KEY|PRIVATE_KEY|AUTH_TOKEN)
WHEN EXPR MISSING:placeholder|example|test|dummy|TODO && PRESENT:ARG.*(KEY|SECRET|PASSWORD|TOKEN|PASS|CREDENTIAL)
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects build-time ARG instructions used to pass secrets during image construction.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Secret Passed via ARG Instruction.
